Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:04.48,PIN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(950,0)}星期一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有…有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是长谷佑树
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请再和我成为朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是长谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然在日记里有写着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到真的会过来打招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我之所以会再次说出以前说过的那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是因为藤宫同学的记忆被完全重置了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是九条一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仅因为一名转学生的出现
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
